item.title: Cleanup
item.description: If you are doing this as part of a workshop using the Event Engine, you can skip this page. Clean up steps The order below is important to remove resources cleanly. Go to AWS CloudFormation console in US West (N. California) Region and delete the root (non-nested) stack that starts with the name tcat-tag-forge-. We had setup the CI/CD pipeline to not auto-delete the test stack to save testing time.
